<template>
 <winWheel :segments="items"></winWheel>
</template>

<script>
import winWheel from 'vue-winwheel'

export default {
  name: "sss-ss",
  components: {
    winWheel: winWheel
  },
  data() {
    return {
      items: [
        {
          textFillStyle: "#fff",
          fillStyle: "#000",
          text: "Prize 1"
        },
        {
          textFillStyle: "#000",
          fillStyle: "#fadede",
          text: "Prize 2"
        },
        {
          textFillStyle: "#fff",
          fillStyle: "#000",
          text: "Prize 3"
        },
        {
          textFillStyle: "#000",
          fillStyle: "#fadede",
          text: "Prize 4"
        },
        {
          textFillStyle: "#fff",
          fillStyle: "#000",
          text: "Prize 5"
        },
        {
          textFillStyle: "#000",
          fillStyle: "#fadede",
          text: "Prize 6"
        },
        {
          textFillStyle: "#fff",
          fillStyle: "#000",
          text: "Prize 7"
        },
        {
          textFillStyle: "#000",
          fillStyle: "#fadede",
          text: "Prize 8"
        }
      ]
    };
  }
};
</script>
